### ============================================================
### Streamedia — REST Client (VS Code)
### ============================================================
### Variáveis globais — ajuste conforme o seu ambiente
### ============================================================

# @host = http://localhost:3000
@host = https://streamedia.app.klawdyo.com
@rootToken = {{$dotenv ROOT_TOKEN}}
@uploadToken = token-retornado-pelo-upload-init
@playToken = token-retornado-pelo-play-init
@videoID = 00000000-0000-4000-0000-000000000001
@tag = teste-video

### ============================================================
### Health & Info
### ============================================================

### Health check
GET {{host}}/healthz

###

### Versão da API (rate limit 10/min)
GET {{host}}/api

### ============================================================
### Documentação (protegida por ROOT_TOKEN)
### ============================================================

### Documentação (Scalar UI)
GET {{host}}/docs
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

###

### OpenAPI spec (JSON)
GET {{host}}/docs/openapi.json
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

### ============================================================
### Playground da API (issue #18) — rota pública
### ============================================================

### Página interativa (auth → upload → eventos SSE → play → players)
GET {{host}}/playground

### ============================================================
### Eventos do pipeline via SSE (autenticado pelo token de upload)
### ============================================================

### Stream de eventos de um vídeo (processing/ready/failed) ao vivo.
### Abra no navegador/curl: a conexão fica aberta recebendo event: + data:.
GET {{host}}/api/events?video_id={{videoID}}&token={{uploadToken}}
Accept: text/event-stream

### ============================================================
### Métricas (Prometheus / OpenTelemetry)
### ============================================================

### Métricas
GET {{host}}/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

### ============================================================
### Upload — Inicialização (Bearer ROOT_TOKEN)
### ============================================================

### Iniciar upload (tag obrigatória; video_id opcional — UUID v7 gerado se omitido)
POST {{host}}/api/upload/init
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

{
  "tag": "{{tag}}",
  "declared_size_bytes": 10485760
}

###

### Iniciar upload com video_id pré-definido
POST {{host}}/api/upload/init
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

{
  "tag": "{{tag}}",
  "video_id": "{{videoID}}",
  "declared_size_bytes": 10485760
}

###

### Iniciar upload com webhook_url customizada por vídeo (issue #20)
### URL HTTPS válida (<= 2048 chars): os webhooks deste vídeo vão para ela
### em vez da WEBHOOK_URL global. Omitida/vazia usa a global.
POST {{host}}/api/upload/init
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

{
  "tag": "{{tag}}",
  "declared_size_bytes": 10485760,
  "webhook_url": "https://hooks.example.com/streamedia/meu-video"
}

### ============================================================
### Upload — Protocolo TUS (autenticado via Upload-Token)
### ============================================================

### TUS: Criar upload (sem video_id — o servidor extrai do token)
POST {{host}}/files/
Upload-Token: {{uploadToken}}
Upload-Length: 10485760
Tus-Resumable: 1.0.0
Content-Length: 0

###

### TUS: Criar upload (com video_id)
POST {{host}}/files/{{videoID}}
Upload-Token: {{uploadToken}}
Upload-Length: 10485760
Tus-Resumable: 1.0.0
Content-Length: 0

###

### TUS: Consultar offset / status do upload
HEAD {{host}}/files/{{videoID}}
Upload-Token: {{uploadToken}}
Tus-Resumable: 1.0.0

###

### TUS: Enviar chunk (PATCH)
# Ajuste Upload-Offset e o body conforme o progresso real
PATCH {{host}}/files/{{videoID}}
Upload-Token: {{uploadToken}}
Tus-Resumable: 1.0.0
Upload-Offset: 0
Content-Type: application/offset+octet-stream

< ./sample-chunk.bin

###

### TUS: Cancelar upload
DELETE {{host}}/files/{{videoID}}
Upload-Token: {{uploadToken}}
Tus-Resumable: 1.0.0

### ============================================================
### Status do vídeo (Bearer ROOT_TOKEN)
### ============================================================

### Consultar status de um vídeo
GET {{host}}/api/status/{{videoID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

### ============================================================
### Playback — HLS Streaming
### ============================================================

### Emitir URL de play (Bearer ROOT_TOKEN) — retorna { video_id, tag, play_url, token, expires_at, resolutions }
POST {{host}}/api/play/init
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

{
  "video_id": "{{videoID}}"
}

###

### Master playlist (autenticada via token de play na query; sem expires)
GET {{host}}/video/{{tag}}/{{videoID}}.m3u8?token={{playToken}}

###

### Playlist de resolução (480 — pública)
GET {{host}}/video/{{tag}}/{{videoID}}/480/playlist.m3u8

###

### Playlist de resolução (720 — pública)
GET {{host}}/video/{{tag}}/{{videoID}}/720/playlist.m3u8

###

### Playlist de resolução (1080 — pública)
GET {{host}}/video/{{tag}}/{{videoID}}/1080/playlist.m3u8

###

### Segmento HLS (exemplo — público)
GET {{host}}/video/{{tag}}/{{videoID}}/720/0.ts

###

### Thumbnail (poster) por resolução — público, sem token (issue #19)
GET {{host}}/video/{{tag}}/{{videoID}}/thumb_480.jpg

### ============================================================
### Admin — Vídeos (Bearer ROOT_TOKEN)
### ============================================================

### Listar vídeos (paginação)
GET {{host}}/admin/videos?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

###

### Listar vídeos por status
GET {{host}}/admin/videos?status=ready&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

###

### Listar vídeos por tag
GET {{host}}/admin/videos?tag={{tag}}&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

###

### Deletar vídeo (banco + arquivos em disco)
DELETE {{host}}/admin/videos/{{videoID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

### ============================================================
### Admin — Fila de transcodificação (Bearer ROOT_TOKEN)
### ============================================================

### Status da fila
GET {{host}}/admin/queue
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

### ============================================================
### Admin — Estatísticas (Bearer ROOT_TOKEN)
### ============================================================

### Estatísticas globais
GET {{host}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}

###

### Estatísticas de um vídeo específico
GET {{host}}/admin/stats?video_id={{videoID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{rootToken}}
